case_circumstances: Unknown black male was found in the dispatcher room at the Church Ave G train station. A train arriving in the station noticed smoke coming from the room and alerted supervisors. When workers went to investigate the smoke and opened the door, there was an explosion. FDNY arrived and put our fire. There were drums of cleaning solution in the room, which were the source of the explosion. The decedent was found in the room after the fire was put out.
